				<h1 class="entry-title"><a href="http://portcolbornelibrary.org/?p=1132" rel="bookmark">Just for Kids</a></h1>

								<div class="entry-meta">
					<span class="posted-on"><i class="fa fa-calendar"></i> <a href="http://portcolbornelibrary.org/?p=1132" rel="bookmark"><time class="entry-date published" datetime="2016-03-06T20:20:35+00:00">March 6, 2016</time><time class="updated" datetime="2016-09-07T09:52:58+00:00">September 7, 2016</time></a></span><span class="byline"> <i class="fa fa-user"></i> <span class="author vcard"><a class="url fn n" href="http://portcolbornelibrary.org/?author=1">admin</a></span></span>
				
				</div><!-- .entry-meta -->
							</header><!-- .entry-header -->

						<div class="entry-content">

					<h2></h2>
<h2>Fine Art Painting for Children</h2>
<div>
<div><strong>Saturday afternoons, beginning September 24, 2016</strong></div>
<div><strong>2:00 p.m. to 4:00 p.m.</strong></div>
<div>For ages 6 to 10. Cost is $15.00 per 2-hour lesson. Space is limited. Pre-register at the library.</div>
<div>
<hr />
</div>
<h2><span style="color: #000000;">Tot Time </span></h2>
<div>
<div><strong>Thursday mornings, 10:00 am to 11:00 a.m.</strong></div>
<div>Crafts, stories &amp; activities. For ages 2 to 4 with their parent/caregivers. Cost is $1.00 per session. Space is limited. <strong>Pre-register at the library.</strong></div>
<div>
<hr />
</div>
</div>
</div>

